node.text:
Kanye West’s DONDA merch - sold exclusively at the album listening party this week - is already reselling online for up to $400

Attendees who purchased shirts say that the transaction went to “Dreamchasers ATL”, a non-profit organisation who provide educational & financial services in the state of Georgia

A quick look at the upcoming heat reactive crocodile leather Heat Sense Shoe from @kitowares 

Set to release early next month, on kito.online.

What are your thoughts on these, cop or drop?

node.text:
LVMH have acquired a 60% stake of Virgil Abloh’s Off-White brand

Abloh maintains a 40% stake and will work creatively on “brands yet to launch” plus other luxury partnerships

Virgil also hopes to use the deal to “expand opportunities for diverse individuals" within the fashion industry

Head to slnofficial.com or click link in bio for more information
